@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam ActivityDiamondFontSize 12

title Nektar Domain Extension — 单次执行链与收敛研究流

|#LightBlue| NektarGateway |
start
:接收 NektarProblemSpec;
note right
  solver_family: ADR / IncNS
  dimension, variables,
  boundary conditions
end note

|#LightGreen| SessionCompiler |
:build_session_plan();
note right
  → NektarSessionPlan
  solver_binary, equation_type,
  expansion, mesh, conditions
end note

|#LightGray| XMLRenderer |
:render_session_xml();
note right
  → session.xml 文件
  可直接输入 Nektar++ 求解器
end note

|#Wheat| SolverExecutor |
:execute_plan();
note right
  调用 Nektar++ 二进制
  捕获 stdout/stderr/log
  提取 error norms, metrics
  → NektarRunArtifact
end note

|#LightCoral| PostprocessComponent |
:run_postprocess();
note right
  FieldConvert -e (误差评估)
  派生文件 (.vtu/.dat)
  收敛 metrics 提取
  → enriched NektarRunArtifact
end note

|#LightSkyBlue| NektarValidator |
:validate_run();
note right
  solver 干净退出检查
  field files 存在性
  error vs reference 比较
  → NektarValidationReport
end note

:单次执行完成;

if (ConvergenceStudy?) then (是)

  |#Orchid| ConvergenceStudyComponent |
  :遍历 axis.values\n(NumModes sweep);
  note right
    deep-copy base_problem
    mutate NumModes per trial
  end note

  repeat
    :_run_single_trial();
    note right
      compile → execute →
      postprocess → validate
      失败时降级为 failed trial report
    end note

    :构建 analyzer evidence;
    note right
      parse_solver_log()
      parse_filter_outputs()
      summarize_reference_error()
      → SolverLogAnalysis
      → FilterOutputAnalysis
      → ErrorSummary
    end note

  repeat while (还有 axis values?\nstop_on_first_pass?)
  ->否;

  :计算 study-level 派生指标;
  note right
    error_sequence
    drop_ratios
    observed_order
    (log(e_i/e_{i+1}) / log(N_{i+1}/N_i))
  end note

  :评估 convergence rule;
  note right
    **absolute**: metric ≤ target_tolerance
    **relative_drop**: ratio ≤ relative_drop_ratio
    **plateau**: |Δratio| < plateau_tolerance
    未命中 → fallback 最佳 metric trial
  end note

  :生成 ConvergenceStudyReport;
  note right
    trials, recommended_value,
    converged, observed_order,
    recommended_reason,
    error_sequence, drop_ratios
  end note

else (否)
endif

stop

@enduml
